skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: river gauge
des: River Gauge will tell you the current water level of many popular paddling rivers around Minnesota, including some in Iowa and Wisconsin. It uses the USGS stream gauge information to tell you the current river height and/or CFS.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
